        What Jensen Huang Has Been Telling Us For Six Months
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-6">The Token Factory thesis — and why every single industry should be paying attention.</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-400 text-sm border-t border-white/10 pt-6">
        <span>Lisa Tamati</span>
        <span class="text-white/20">|</span>
        <span>01/05/2026</span>
      </div>
    </div>

